column3: “It a nice strain, packed a bowl in my bong just to taste it and try it out, very good i was at a steady nice chill high for a good 2 and a half hours before i need to smoke a few more bowls and after the next bowls I was pretty lit, I am going back to this bud the next time I was some tree”

“Real good strain if you have high tolerance. The guy I got it from told me there weren't reviews so I just put a little in my pipe to test it and ive been high up for 3 hours now. Strong shit right here. This is the sticky icky i been lookin for”
“My wife and I smoked a pre roll from a dispensary and we didn't move for a long time lol.”
“honestly the name says it all a it will you for the ride of your life but its not perfect still a very relaxing and chill high”
“This strain is a easy mid not good but not bad”
